&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;About VTEX&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt;VTEX (NYSE: VTEX) is the composable and complete commerce platform that delivers more efficiency and less maintenance to organizations seeking to make smarter IT investments and modernize their tech stack. Through our pragmatic composability approach, we empower brands, distributo

&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;You will own the digital presence of Battle of Bats — end to end. Instagram, YouTube, player stories, match content, behind-the-scenes, reels, thumbnails, captions. All of it.&lt;br&gt;This is not a support role. You will be the engine behind our entire digital show.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;*For this position you are required to attend the office 4 days a week (Monday - Thursday), and remote work on Friday.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you&#39;ll own&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Our &lt;strong&gt;Instagram&lt;/strong&gt; — entertaining, consistent, and built to grow fast&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Our &lt;strong&gt;YouTube&lt;/strong&gt; channel — from match highlights to player documentaries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Player stories&lt;/strong&gt; — pros and amateurs alike, told in a way that stops people scrolling and goes viral&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Behind-the-scenes content from training, matches, and everything in between&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Short-form video, long-form video, captions, thumbnails — the full stack&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Audience retention&lt;/strong&gt; — you care about people watching to the end, not just clicking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;About the Team&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Battle of Bats is building the greatest cricket show the world has ever seen. Our goal is simple: the most entertaining cricket experience audiences have seen in years. We&#39;re not a league. We&#39;re not a tournament. We&#39;re an entertainment brand — and cricket is our stage.&lt;br&gt;In 2027, we bring together three teams — India, USA and Universe — for three days of cricket, rivalry, and storytelling. Every match is content. Every story matters.&lt;br&gt;We&#39;re a small, ambitious team and we&#39;re looking for our next key player.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Who you are&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A generalist — you can shoot, edit, write, and post&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Obsessed with cricket and with how stories are told online&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You understand what makes people stop scrolling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;ve grown (or helped grow) a social account before&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fast, autonomous, and proactive — you don&#39;t wait to be told&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You think in content series, not just individual posts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Why this role is different&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You won&#39;t be producing content for a corporation — you&#39;ll be building a show from the ground up&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your work will be seen by cricket fans across India, the US, and the world&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;ll work directly with the founders — your ideas will actually be used&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In March 2027, you&#39;ll be on the ground at the event itself&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;ll help create something that has never been done in cricket before&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Logistics&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full-time position&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relocation required — you must be available and willing to move&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel is part of the role, including being on the ground at the event in March 2027&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;About VTEX&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;VTEX (NYSE: VTEX) is the composable and complete commerce platform that delivers more efficiency and less maintenance to organizations seeking to make smarter IT investments and modernize their tech stack. Through our pragmatic composability approach, we empower brands, distributors, and retailers with unparalleled flexibility and comprehensive solutions, enabling them to invest solely in what provides a clear business ad

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Data Engineer on the Data Platform team, you&#39;ll help design, build, and evolve the data infrastructure that powers analytics, AI, and machine learning across VTEX. This is a hands-on, mid-level role: you&#39;ll own features end-to-end — from ingestion and processing to storage and consumption — taking on problems that come with real ambiguity, and delivering them with growing independence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re not looking for someone who arrives knowing everything. We&#39;re looking for someone with a strong engineering foundation and a high ceiling: a fast learner with sharp problem-solving instincts who is energized by a data platform going through a deep transformation of its architecture and the way it&#39;s built.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HOW WE WORK&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The way we build has changed completely in the last year, and this role is defined by it. On this team, you don&#39;t measure yourself by lines of code written — you measure yourself by the value and quality of what you ship. AI tools are part of every step of our work: we direct them, review their output critically, and are accountable for the result.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That makes two things essential:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leveraging AI to scale your impact.&lt;/strong&gt; We expect you to use AI extensively and well — designing workflows where agents handle the &quot;known-knowns&quot; (standard ETL, repetitive modeling) so your judgment goes to the hard, ambiguous problems. The goal is genuine leverage: producing at a level that simply wasn&#39;t possible a year ago.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clarity as a contract.&lt;/strong&gt; The quality of your written word is the quality of your AI output. If you can&#39;t describe a transformation clearly in a spec or doc, the code isn&#39;t ready to be written — by you or an agent. Strong technical writing and spec-driven thinking aren&#39;t &quot;nice to have&quot; here; they&#39;re how the work gets done and how it scales to teammates and agents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE TEAM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data Platform is the team inside VTEX&#39;s Data &amp;amp; Analytics org that builds the foundation the rest of the company&#39;s data products are built on. We&#39;re in the middle of a deep transformation: migrating from a Redshift-centric warehouse to a multi-engine Data Lakehouse on Apache Iceberg, moving our infrastructure to EKS, and re-architecting ingestion for scale and cost. We run a lot of initiatives in parallel, with high autonomy and a high quality bar.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You won&#39;t be siloed on one thing. You&#39;ll typically own at least one larger initiative while moving smaller improvements forward alongside it. Depending on where you fit best, your work could span:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data ingestion&lt;/strong&gt; — migrating high-volume pipelines from Kinesis/Firehose to our new Kafka/AutoMQ-on-EKS stack.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lakehouse migration &amp;amp; evolution&lt;/strong&gt; — moving workloads onto Iceberg, Spark (EMR-on-EKS) processing, and new maintenance and consumption tooling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platform infrastructure&lt;/strong&gt; — Kubernetes/EKS, compute efficiency, reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Query &amp;amp; consumption&lt;/strong&gt; — engines like Trino, Cube, DuckDB, and Athena, and smart routing across them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platform tech debt, observability, and engineering-process improvements&lt;/strong&gt; that keep the platform fast, reliable, and cost-efficient.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll also have the opportunity to join the team&#39;s on-call rotation, helping keep a platform that ingests billions of events a day healthy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHO YOU ARE&

&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;44&quot; data-end=&quot;318&quot;&gt;At VTEX, we believe in the power of data to drive strategic decisions and create smart automations that optimize our global operations. We are looking for an intern who is passionate about data, technology, and innovation to join our Data Strategy team.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;In this role, you will have the opportunity to work with tools such as Power BI, n8n, Excel and actively participate in projects exploring the use of Generative AI to integrate and automate internal processes. This is an excellent opportunity for those who want to learn and work in a global company with a digital-first mindset.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;WHAT YOU WILL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain Power BI dashboards for different areas of the company;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support data analysis and the development of actionable insights;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with multidisciplinary teams on strategic projects focused on efficiency;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in initiatives involving the integration of processes with generative AIs (such as using LLMs for autonomous agents, summarizations, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;WHO YOU ARE&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1528&quot; data-end=&quot;1546&quot;&gt;Currently enrolled in an undergraduate program (Engineering, Computer Science, Statistics or related fields);&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1528&quot; data-end=&quot;1546&quot;&gt;Basic knowledge of Excel/Google Sheets;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1528&quot; data-end=&quot;1546&quot;&gt;Intermediate understanding of Power BI (or another BI tool);&lt;/li&gt;
