Ps, developing technical documentation, building proof of concepts (PoCs), and leading technical conversations through to contract signature. Once the deal is closed, you will facilitate a thorough handover of project context and documentation to the Customer Experience (CX) team to ensure a smooth implementation.&lt;br&gt;This role is ideal for a self-driven, solution-oriented professional who is passionate about digital commerce and excited by the opportunity to shape transformative commerce experiences for enterprise clients.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*For this position you are required to attend the office 4 days a week (Monday - Thursday), and remote work on Friday.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who you are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
