&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;As a Senior Backend Engineer, you will serve as a technical reference for the team, providing guidance and expertise in backend development best practices. You will be responsible for important evolutions of our products in terms of scalability (they&#39;re global products!)&amp;nbsp; and product evolution to address main customers demands and market opportunities. Your contributions will directly impact the success and global growth of our organization, making this a truly exciting opportunity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
