&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;39:1-39:454;3612-4065&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll take on one of our hardest engineering challenges: evolving our Service Mesh. Today VTEX runs a custom, highly performant router (built in .NET) that acts as our service mesh, processing millions of requests per second as the backbone for every VTEX application. Your mission is to help evolve this mission-critical infrastructure toward a market-standard stack (like Istio) with zero downtime and the reliability thousands of stores depend on.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
