&lt;h3&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Staff Product Manager for Ads, you will play a key role in shaping VTEX’s Retail Media and Ads platform, helping build a scalable media hub that enables brands and industries to activate 360° media strategies directly within commerce experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role focuses on Onsite Ads, where VTEX operates as a media buying engine, connecting advertisers, retailers, and shoppers across high-impact commerce touchpoints. You will lead the product vision and execution for a domain that already serves major global brands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With a strong focus on stakeholder management, strategy, and execution, you will ensure the Ads product evolves toward a 2026 vision, balancing short-term performance needs with long-term platform scalability — including the impact of LLMs and AI on the ads and retail media ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;WHAT YOU WILL DO&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and evolve the Onsite Ads product, acting as the guardian of its long-term vision and ensuring alignment with VTEX’s revenue and growth strategy.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and execute the product roadmap for the next 6–12 months, while shaping a clear and scalable 2026 vision for Retail Media at VTEX.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex customer and business needs into clear product priorities, ensuring visibility and alignment across Engineering, Sales, Customer Success, and Growth teams.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with advertisers, retailers, and internal stakeholders to balance performance, campaign needs, and platform evolution.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Engineering to deliver high-impact solutions, leveraging your technical background and understanding of ads and media systems.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Customer Success to improve how clients engage with the Ads product, clarifying ownership, flows, and expectations around product-related topics.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate and incorporate the impact of AI and LLMs on ads performance, campaign optimization, and media buying workflows.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support internal team evolution, including collaboration with future PM roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
