&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced Product Manager with a&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;proven track record in managing complex, large-scale ecosystems.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to build and communicate product vision, translating strategy into execution in complex, multi-stakeholder environments.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
